HEADWORD: Potcher
<hw>Potch"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or that
which, potches.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Potcher engine</b></col> <fld>(Paper Making)</fld>, <cd>a
